{"tid":1377871,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"升級！進步！戰後檢討！","createTime":"2019-07-28T14:44:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-28T14:48:47.000Z","uid":76543,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"f1e567b1d9250fc03fb355db7eebf92836f5f8eb","tid":1377871,"uid":76543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T14:44:59.000Z","msg":"我覺得每一次都要做到有戰後檢討<br />\n好坦白 我哋爭取緊一個<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">民主同自由</span></span></strong>嘅社會<br />\n民主社會應該<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">尊重大家意見</span></span></strong> <br />\n我明白前線勇武個心好急切<br />\n但係 應該係以理服人 而唔係一句我係前線就大晒<br />\n冷氣軍師都一樣 你可以俾意見 幫佢哋諗點退 而唔係落order咁叫人撤 屌柒人哋做咩唔走<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">記住 不割蓆 不分化 不篤灰</span></span></strong><br />\n所以兩邊都俾下意見 聽下意見 唔好一嚟就互屌<br />\n一場運動最易失敗嘅原因就一定係內哄<br />\n所以我哋唔好互屌 試下每次都嚟個戰後檢討<br />\n<br />\n例如：<br />\n<br />\n勇武：用火好好 因為狗好難升級武力 我哋仲有無限可能 <span style=\"color: teal;\">(試下唔好太戀戰 be water 呢個一定多人唔同意 再傾好唔好)</span><br />\n<br />\n和理非：喺狗鐵試下唔好留錢 直接買好多張15.5嘅飛留低 咁就唔洗排長龍<br />\n<br />\n冷氣軍師：組織好情報 唔好落order叫人走 試下留低逃生路線幫佢哋<br />\n<br />\n我可能打到1999 希望大家明白<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港<br />\n時代革命</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"00c05bafdc064fce939463f09af48ba71bb96b60","tid":1377871,"uid":76543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T14:45:10.000Z","msg":"自推十下"},{"pid":"7f9fe93b01d9d2de002e363c6bd449386f470c6d","tid":1377871,"uid":76543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T14:45:20.000Z","msg":"光復香港"},{"pid":"1a61afa8cc9f0a713123a9b2203044c74d4afdec","tid":1377871,"uid":76543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T14:45:30.000Z","msg":"時代革命"},{"pid":"b4cee3d128c0cc257877fa068f98e651d091436c","tid":1377871,"uid":76543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T14:45:41.000Z","msg":"光復香港"},{"pid":"7758a66b5cbf28bb5230659206d037833ff6ba9e","tid":1377871,"uid":76543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T14:45:52.000Z","msg":"時代革命"},{"pid":"197dc2397b505b6b550bcf308186426432434418","tid":1377871,"uid":235374,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T14:45:54.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><br />\n經濟學抗爭原則 遲d出post<br />\n唔需要更強武器 點都唔會夠打 人地太多資源 而係策略問題 <br />\n一班人要不斷轉陣地 周圍搞破壞 搞完就走 <br />\n唔好set路障企係到 同等比人拉無分別 唔夠打就閃<br />\n</span></span>"},{"pid":"2616d2e29a2007014bea170727e60087219b53e8","tid":1377871,"uid":76543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T14:46:25.000Z","msg":"不割蓆"},{"pid":"a8d74a891df86109ffe424938c1bccc5491ebd07","tid":1377871,"uid":76543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T14:46:35.000Z","msg":"不篤灰"},{"pid":"bff91c3987b07b6a34f0d9c86da8fb70f5aab2bb","tid":1377871,"uid":76543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T14:46:47.000Z","msg":"不分化"},{"pid":"d5bae1ebcf0d446b8c524c71b4176c23b9833dc7","tid":1377871,"uid":76543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T14:46:59.000Z","msg":"唔好再互屌"},{"pid":"d6f704929e04d138bfec687b4fd723485acbdff2","tid":1377871,"uid":292733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T14:47:40.000Z","msg":"【支持香港警察！！！】<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1377658\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1377658</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"c9815e8995d7bd9fc81731b9c1d16be177252317","tid":1377871,"uid":41813,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T14:47:47.000Z","msg":"未到戰後<br />\n戰後再推"},{"pid":"0bc7f924998c5c0fd66f8e5141c90aef6ce45ae9","tid":1377871,"uid":76543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T14:48:42.000Z","msg":"戰後再推 一係我戰後再開 大家依家關注前線 多謝"},{"pid":"286b6765536c781777ba1a7a10b3ef2cef203601","tid":1377871,"uid":210612,"like